=\"#EEEEEE\"|''Vacant''\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|rowspan=\"12\" style=\"background:{{Democratic-Republican Party/meta/color}};\"|\n|data-sort-value=\"Tayler, John\"|[[John Tayler]]<br><small>(acting from January 29, 1811)</small>\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|data-sort-value=\"Clinton, DeWitt\"|[[DeWitt Clinton]]<br><small>(elected May 2, 1811)</small>\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1813|1813]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" data-sort-value=\"Tayler, John\"|[[John Tayler]]\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1816|1816]]<br>{{efn|Tompkins resigned to be [[Vice President of the United States]]. As lieutenant governor, Tayler acted as governor until a successor was elected.}}\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|5\n|data-sort-value=\"Tayler, John\"|[[File:John_Tayler,_governor_of_New_York_(portrait_by_Ezra_Ames).png|75px]]\n!scope=\"row\"|[[John Tayler]]<br><small>(Acting)</small>\n|{{dts|February 24, 1817}}<br/>\u2013<br/>June 30, 1817\n|[[Democratic-Republican Party|Democratic\u2013<br>Republican]]\n|data-sort-value=\"Swift, Philetus\"|[[Philetus Swift]]<br><small>(acting)</small>\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"|6\n|rowspan=\"2\" data-sort-value=\"Clinton, DeWitt\"|[[File:DeWitt_Clinton_by_Rembrandt_Peale.jpg|75px]]\n!rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"row\"|[[DeWitt Clinton]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|{{dts|July 1, 1817}}<br/>\u2013<br/>December 31, 1822\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Democratic-Republican Party|Democratic\u2013<br>Republican]]\n|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1817|1817]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" data-sort-value=\"Tayler, John\"|[[John Tayler]]\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1820|1820]]\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|7\n|data-sort-value=\"Yates, Joseph\"|[[File:JosephCYates.jpg|75px]]\n!scope=\"row\"|[[Joseph C. Yates]]\n|{{dts|January 1, 1823}}<br/>\u2013<br/>December 31, 1824\n|[[Democratic-Republican Party|Democratic\u2013<br>Republican]]\n|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1822|1822]]\n|data-sort-