roop, Enos\"|[[File:EThroop.png|75px]]\n!rowspan=\"3\" scope=\"row\"|[[Enos T. Throop]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|{{dts|March 12, 1829}}<br/>\u2013<br/>December 31, 1832\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|data-sort-value=\"Stebbins, Charles\"|[[Charles Stebbins]]<br><small>(acting)</small>\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|data-sort-value=\"Oliver, William\"|[[William M. Oliver]]<br><small>(acting)</small>\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1830|1830]]\n|data-sort-value=\"Livingston, Edward\"|[[Edward Philip Livingston]]\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|rowspan=\"3\"|11\n|rowspan=\"3\" data-sort-value=\"Marcy, William\"|[[File:WMarcy.png|75px]]\n!rowspan=\"3\" scope=\"row\"|[[William L. Marcy]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|{{dts|January 1, 1833}}<br/>\u2013<br/>December 31, 1838\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1832|1832]]\n|rowspan=\"3\" data-sort-value=\"Tracy, John\"|[[John Tracy (politician)|John Tracy]]\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1834|1834]]\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1836|1836]]\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"|12\n|rowspan=\"2\" data-sort-value=\"Seward, William\"|[[File:Henry_Inman_-_William_H._Seward.jpg|75px]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" bgcolor={{Whig Party (United States)/meta/color}}|\n!rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"row\"|[[William H. Seward]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|{{dts|January 1, 1839}}<br/>\u2013<br/>December 31, 1842\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Whig Party (United States)|Whig]]\n|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1838|1838]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" bgcolor={{Whig Party (United States)/meta/color}}|\n|rowspan=\"2\" data-sort-value=\"Bradish, Luther\"|[[Luther Bradish]]\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|[[New York gubernatorial election, 1840|1840]]\n|- style=\"height:2em;\"\n|13\n|data-sort-value=\"Bouck, William\"|[[File:WBouck.png|75px]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" style=\"background:{{Democratic Party (United States)/meta/color}};\"|\n!